123
00:12:42,580 --> 00:12:47,110
but was it really...really because of Hyeon Ho?

124
00:12:51,470 --> 00:12:52,990
Okay.

125
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:56,710
I'll be honest.

126
00:12:58,120 --> 00:13:04,240
All the things I received from your family...

127
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:08,330
Money, piano...

128
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:15,140
Because of all that, I never dared to think about having you.

129
00:13:18,420 --> 00:13:21,790
I received a lot from your family,

130
00:13:21,790 --> 00:13:24,270
so even when I didn't want to see you, I...

131
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:40,400
So...just let me go.

132
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:44,210
Please just let me go.

133
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:49,460
From now on,

134
