138
00:14:26,970 --> 00:14:29,180
- Did you do that?
 - Yeah.

139
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:35,810
I did.

140
00:14:42,490 --> 00:14:45,950
Joon Young, no matter what you say,

141
00:14:45,950 --> 00:14:48,910
