177
00:18:38,820 --> 00:18:42,560
- That...
 - From Jung Kyung.

178
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:47,810
Joon Young...

179
00:18:49,630 --> 00:18:52,910
I... I really didn't know.

180
00:18:52,910 --> 00:18:54,660
Joon Young, no...

181
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:56,820
Your dad probably...

182
00:18:56,820 --> 00:19:00,250
He probably called her because he had no other way...

183
00:19:00,250 --> 00:19:02,870
Why did we take Jung Kyung's money again?

184
00:19:04,330 --> 00:19:05,850
Why?

185
00:19:07,740 --> 00:19:10,900
I begged you guys.

186
00:19:10,900 --> 00:19:16,220
Please... please stop making me look so pathetic.

187
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:19,280
I begged you.

188
00:19:19,280 --> 00:19:23,760
But... once again, Jung Kyung...

189
00:19:25,820 --> 00:19:28,370
No... Joon Young...

190
00:19:28,370 --> 00:19:31,040
If Dad didn't keep doing that...

191
00:19:31,830 --> 00:19:34,240
If he didn't take the money...

192
00:19:37,540 --> 00:19:39,480
I might have...

193
00:19:41,430 --> 00:19:44,050
At the very least, I may have

194
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:47,620
become a lot happier than I am now.

