217
00:22:23,590 --> 00:22:26,330
You guys left in a taxi.

218
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:32,060
Where did you go?

219
00:22:38,260 --> 00:22:45,780
I was Jung Kyung's accompanist yesterday, and then we had to go to Professor Song Jung Hee's house for something.

220
00:22:49,700 --> 00:22:54,710
Why did you go there with her?

221
00:22:57,210 --> 00:23:00,550
We had something to do.

222
00:23:05,960 --> 00:23:07,740
And...

223
00:23:12,470 --> 00:23:15,050
 Did you... send him money? 

224
00:23:16,360 --> 00:23:17,940
 Yeah. 

225
00:23:20,540 --> 00:23:22,650
 I did. 

226
00:23:29,850 --> 00:23:35,220
Then, I went home and my mom came. That's all.

227
00:23:37,150 --> 00:23:43,220
Sorry. I didn't think it was significant enough for me to tell you...

228
00:23:43,220 --> 00:23:45,750
It keeps bothering me.

229
00:23:46,800 --> 00:23:50,120
That fact that you're Jung Kyung's accompanist bothers me.

230
00:23:52,590 --> 00:23:59,250
I told myself I'm worried about nothing, and I wanted to trust you and not think about it...

231
00:24:00,900 --> 00:24:03,570
I thought everything would turn out fine...

232
00:24:05,730 --> 00:24:07,920
but it's not fine.

233
00:24:12,780 --> 00:24:14,820
I'm sorry.

234
00:24:16,530 --> 00:24:21,670
And... you don't have to worry about it anymore.

235
00:24:22,870 --> 00:24:25,760
I'm not going to be Jung Kyung's accompanist anymore.

236
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:31,210
I shouldn't have done it from the start,

237
00:24:34,500 --> 00:24:37,020
but I guess I didn't think it through properly.

238
00:24:43,230 --> 00:24:44,470
You're here.

239
00:24:44,470 --> 00:24:46,070
Oh, how have you been?

240
00:24:46,070 --> 00:24:48,020
Thanks for making the time to come here today.

241
00:24:48,020 --> 00:24:50,830
